This paper discusses the vulnerabilities in the NFC-Android ecosystem, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the need for privacy awareness and risks associated with using contactless services, which can be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cybercrime (cs.CY).
